phrases.phrase: 양이 많아서 도저히 다 먹을 수 없었다.
meanings: 식후의 표현 The portions were so big I couldn't eat it all.
식후의 표현 The portions were so large I couldn't finish it all.
식후의 표현 I can't eat any more.
식후의 표현 I can't eat another bite.
레스토랑 SOS I can't eat this.
주문하기 Can I eat dinner now?
